            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"the-great-convergence\">The Great Convergence</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Life expectancy at birth in 1960 vs 2023 for 21 countries. Sixty years ago, a child born in Japan could expect 34 more years of life than one born in Afghanistan. Today that gap has narrowed to 18 years.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
